In this project i am using ESP32 as source board and 4 DC motor connected with L298N motor driver and for power supply 12v of external battery is used.
We are using an application to control car and the apk file is being added you just have to upload the ip address that have been generated after uploading the code in ESP32.
Pin Connection are 
motor driver                     ESP32
Enable/speed motors Right        GPIO14(D5)
Enable/speed motors Left         GPIO12(D6)
L298N in1 motors Rightx          GPIO15(D8)
L298N in2 motors Right           GPIO13(D7)
L298N in3 motors Left            GPIO2(D4)
L298N in4 motors Left            GPIO0(D3)
